    <title>Python 学习笔记</title>
    <url>/2021/11/05/Python%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="Python-学习笔记"><a href="#Python-学习笔记" class="headerlink" title="Python 学习笔记"></a>Python 学习笔记</h1><p>本文基于 Python 3.9.1 ，是记录我 Python 学习的笔记。</p>
<p>本文省略环境搭建，IDE等步骤。</p>
<span id="more"></span>

<hr>
<h1 id="Hello-World"><a href="#Hello-World" class="headerlink" title="Hello World"></a>Hello World</h1><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="string">&quot;Hello World&quot;</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>是不是非常简单，对比一下 Java。</p>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">HelloWorld</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">(String[] args)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        System.out.println(<span class="string">&quot;Hello World&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>Java 便显得十分麻烦了。</p>
<hr>
<h1 id="基础语法"><a href="#基础语法" class="headerlink" title="基础语法"></a>基础语法</h1><h2 id="编码"><a href="#编码" class="headerlink" title="编码"></a>编码</h2><p>在 Python 3 以后，默认使用 UTF-8 编码，在此之前需要在文件头写入一行代码。</p>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># -*- coding=utf-8 -*-</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>虽然现在默认 UTF-8 编码，但是仍推荐在文件头写入该代码。</p>
<hr>
<h2 id="注释"><a href="#注释" class="headerlink" title="注释"></a>注释</h2><p>注释正如其名，对一行代码进行解释，在解释器运行代码过程中，会自动省略注释。</p>
<p>注释分为单行注释与多行注释。</p>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 我是单行注释</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;&quot;&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">我是多行注释</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">Hello World</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;&quot;&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>在写代码过程中，推荐添加注释，不仅让人了解你的 API 使用方法，也整理了自己的思路。</p>
<hr>
<h2 id="变量"><a href="#变量" class="headerlink" title="变量"></a>变量</h2><p>变量相当于数学中的未知数，可以为任何值。</p>
<p>新建变量后，解释器会在系统内存中，划分一段内存，并将值储存在内存中。当调用变量时，解释器就会在对应变量的地址内返回对应值（可能有点不准确，我也是编程新手）</p>
<p>在 Python 中，变量不需要指定类型，只需要赋值就可以了。但也带来的不良后果，例如在 Java 这种编译型语言中，可以提前好指定类型，不需要进行赋值，而在Python 中，新建变量也必须赋值。</p>
<p>赋值变量的语法为</p>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">x = <span class="number">10</span></span><br><span class="line">y = <span class="string">&#x27;Hello World&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">z = <span class="literal">True</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(x) <span class="comment"># 输出 10</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(y) <span class="comment"># 输出 Hello World</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(z) <span class="comment"># 输出 True</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>变量起名也有规范：只能使用下划线、数字、字母，且数字不能开头，变量名不能为字面值（关键字）</p>
<p>在编写代码过程中，对于变量的起名遵循下划线命名格式，如：<code>hello_world</code>, <code>is_at_all</code></p>
<hr>
<h2 id="行与缩进"><a href="#行与缩进" class="headerlink" title="行与缩进"></a>行与缩进</h2><p>在 Python 中，每一行末尾不需要加 “;” 。</p>
<p>在其它语言中，代码块用 {} 或  <code>do...end</code> 来表示，但在 Python 中，使用缩进来表示代码块：</p>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> <span class="literal">True</span>:</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="string">&quot;Hello World&quot;</span>); <span class="comment"># 这里缩进不对会报错</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<hr>
<h1 id="基础数据类型"><a href="#基础数据类型" class="headerlink" title="基础数据类型"></a>基础数据类型</h1><p>Python 有六个基本数据类型，分别为：<strong>数字（Number）</strong>， <strong>字符串（String）</strong>， <strong>列表（List）</strong>， <strong>元组（Tuple）</strong>，<strong>集合（Set）</strong>，<strong>字典（Dictionary）</strong>。</p>
<p>其中不可变数据为：<strong>数字（Number）</strong>，<strong>字符串（String）</strong>，<strong>元组（Tuple）</strong>。</p>
<p>可变数据为：<strong>列表（List）</strong>，<strong>集合（Set）</strong>，<strong>字典（Dictionary）</strong>。</p>
<hr>
<h2 id="数字（Number）"><a href="#数字（Number）" class="headerlink" title="数字（Number）"></a>数字（Number）</h2><p>数字（Number）中有以下几种类型：<strong>整数（int）</strong>，<strong>浮点数（float）</strong>，<strong>布尔数（bool）</strong>，<strong>复数（complex）</strong></p>
<p>在 Python 中，没有 long, short, byte 等类型，但是可以进行类型转换</p>
<p>示例:</p>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">a = <span class="number">114514</span></span><br><span class="line">b = <span class="number">3.14</span></span><br><span class="line">c = <span class="literal">True</span></span><br><span class="line">d = <span class="number">4</span> + <span class="number">3j</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="built_in">type</span>(a)) <span class="comment"># int</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="built_in">type</span>(b)) <span class="comment"># float</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="built_in">type</span>(c)) <span class="comment"># bool</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="built_in">type</span>(d)) <span class="comment"># complex</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<hr>
<h3 id="数值运算符"><a href="#数值运算符" class="headerlink" title="数值运算符"></a>数值运算符</h3><table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th align="center">运算符</th>
<th align="center">含义</th>
<th align="center">举例</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody><tr>
<td align="center">+</td>
<td align="center">加法</td>
<td align="center">1 + 1 = 2</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="center">-</td>
<td align="center">减法</td>
<td align="center">2 - 1 = 1</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="center">*</td>
<td align="center">乘法</td>
<td align="center">1 * 1  = 1</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="center">/</td>
<td align="center">除法（返回浮点数）</td>
<td align="center">4 / 2 = 2.0</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="center">//</td>
<td align="center">除法（返回整数）</td>
<td align="center">4 // 2 = 2</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="center">%</td>
<td align="center">取余</td>
<td align="center">3 / 2 = 1</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="center">**</td>
<td align="center">乘方</td>
<td align="center">2 ** 3 = 8</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
<hr>
<h2 id="字符串"><a href="#字符串" class="headerlink" title="字符串"></a>字符串</h2><p>Python 中的字符串与 JavaScript 一样，字符串使用 <code>‘ ’</code> 或 <code>“ ”</code> 表示 ，示例</p>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">x = <span class="string">&quot;This is X&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">y = <span class="string">&#x27;This is Y&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(x) <span class="comment"># This is X</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(y) <span class="comment"># This is Y</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>字符串本身不可变，但是你可以将变量指向的内存位置改变从而改变字符串值</p>
<hr>
<h3 id="字符串拼接"><a href="#字符串拼接" class="headerlink" title="字符串拼接"></a>字符串拼接</h3><p>字符串拼接采用 <code>+</code></p>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">x = <span class="string">&#x27;Hello, I am &#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(x + <span class="string">&#x27;Python&#x27;</span>) <span class="comment"># Hello, I am Python</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<hr>
<h3 id="字符串格式化"><a href="#字符串格式化" class="headerlink" title="字符串格式化"></a>字符串格式化</h3><p>在 Python3.x 后，有了一种更简便的格式化方法</p>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">x = <span class="string">&#x27;Python&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">y = <span class="string">&#x27;&#123;&#125;, I am &#123;&#125;&#x27;</span>.<span class="built_in">format</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;Hello&#x27;</span>, x)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(y) <span class="comment"># Hello, I am Python</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<p>#施工中</p>
]]></content>
